*nikola-7.7.1 (15 Sep 2015)

  15 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> +nikola-7.7.1.ebuild:
  Add version 7.7.1

  09 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> metadata.xml:
  Update metadata.xml(s) and IUSE(s).

  09 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> nikola-7.6.4.ebuild, nikola-7.7.0.ebuild:
  Trivial fixes for QA.

  09 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> nikola-7.6.4.ebuild, nikola-7.7.0.ebuild:
  Update ebuild file format from "# $Header: $" to "# $Id"

   Since Gentoo changes the VCS from CVS to git, ebuild header is changed.

*nikola-7.7.0 (04 Sep 2015)

  04 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> +nikola-7.7.0.ebuild:
  Add version 7.7.0.

  22 Aug 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> nikola-7.6.4.ebuild:
  Fix to add a necessary dep sys-libs/gdbm.

   Nikola use GNU dbm through Python.
  So Added PYTHON_REQ_USE="gdbm".

*nikola-7.6.4 (22 Aug 2015)

  22 Aug 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> -nikola-7.5.1.ebuild, -nikola-7.6.0.ebuild,
  -nikola-7.6.1.ebuild, -nikola-7.6.2.ebuild, -nikola-7.6.3.ebuild,
  +nikola-7.6.4.ebuild:
  Add version 7.6.4, Delete old versions 7.5.1, 7.6.{0..3}.

