*nikola-7.5.1 (13 Jun 2015)

  13 Jun 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> +nikola-7.5.1.ebuild:
  Add version 7.5.1.

    Nikola version 7.5.1 has been released.
   CHANGES is at https://github.com/getnikola/nikola/blob/v7.5.1/CHANGES.txt

  13 Jun 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> nikola-7.4.1.ebuild, nikola-7.5.0.ebuild:
  Use https:// instead of git:// for live build.

  11 Jun 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> nikola-7.5.0.ebuild:
  7.5.0: Remove USE="livereload".

    ** livereload is obsolete now, use websocket (ws4py). **

  11 Jun 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> nikola-7.4.1.ebuild:
  7.4.1: Specify the yapsy version 1.10.423 dependency.

  11 Jun 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> nikola-7.4.1.ebuild:
  7.4.1: Remove deps for testing use.

  11 Jun 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> -nikola-7.3.1.ebuild, -nikola-7.4.0.ebuild:
  Delete old versions 7.3.1 and 7.4.0.

