*nikola-7.3.1 (08 Mar 2015)

  08 Mar 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> metadata.xml, nikola-7.2.0.ebuild,
  nikola-7.3.0.ebuild, +nikola-7.3.1.ebuild:
  Add version 7.3.1.

   Version bump.
   See https://github.com/getnikola/nikola/releases/tag/v7.3.1

   nikola-7.3.1 depends on dev-python/python-dateutil-2.4.1
  dev-python/python-dateutil-2.4.1 will be newly added to this repository.

